entry_requirements_raw.SPM: Aggregate of 20 points or less across 5 academic subjects.  Non academic subject e.g. Bahasa Melayu, English, Pendidikan Islam etc
entry_requirements_raw.O-Level: 2 Passes (C) at GCSEs.  Non academic subject e.g. Bahasa Melayu, English, Pendidikan Islam etc

course_content.core:
Course Structure Students take eight units over two semesters (four each semester). The three compulsory English units are offered each semester (English A is a prerequisite for English B).  Core Units Complete the following 3 units FSP001 – English A 
FSP002 – English B 
FSP015 – Australian Histories, Institutions and Cultures. FSP001 – English A FSP002 – English B FSP015 – Australian Histories, Institutions and Cultures.
